Summary Figures






Increasing Species

Bald Eagle, Harlequin Duck, Mallard, Northern Cardinal


Species showing no change

Dark-eyed Junco, Red-breasted Merganser, Red-breasted Nuthatch, Hairy Woodpecker, Song Sparrow


Decreasing Species

Common Raven, American Black Duck, American Tree Sparrow, Brown-headed Cowbird, White-winged Scoter

Gulls: Herring Gull, Great Black-backed Gull

Boreal species: Boreal Chickadee, Canada Jay, Spruce Grouse
